<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>DomaHub - Domain Name Rentals</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/min/main_index.min.css" />
  <meta name="description" content="DomaHub provides domain name rentals at low, affordable prices and flexible time slots. Rent one today!" />
  <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>
  <section id="index-img" class="section is-index-img">
    <span></span>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content has-text-centered margin-bottom-25">
        <h1 class="title is-1 is-white">
          Exceptional domains for rent.
        </h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle is-4 is-white">
          Rent memorable domain names for marketing or personal use for the exact duration you need.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <form class="beta-form has-text-centered">
        <p class="signup-text">Please submit your email to apply for our service.</p>
        <div class="control is-grouped-center margin-bottom-0">
          <p class="control margin-right-5 has-icon">
            <input tabindex="1" class="input is-medium" type="text" name="betaemail" placeholder="owner@greatdomains.com"/>
            <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
          </p>
          <p class="control">
            <button tabindex="1" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-stylish">Apply</button>
          </p>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="beta-form-success is-hidden">
        <div class="notification has-text-centered is-white">
          <p>You have been put on the waiting list!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="learn-more-arrow">
      <a tabindex="1" href="#decision-section" id="learn-more-button" title="Learn More">
        <span class="icon is-medium is-white">
          <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="decision-section" class="section is-medium-top">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tabs-box">
        <ul>
          <li id="have-domains-tab" class="is-active">
            <a tabindex="1" href="#owners" title="Domain Owners">I have domains</a>
          </li>
          <li id="want-domains-tab">
            <a tabindex="1" href="#renters" title="Domain Renters">I want domains</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="have-domains-section" class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered margin-bottom-50">Exceptional domain names.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content margin-bottom-20">
            <h2>What makes a domain name exceptional?</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase is-primary">Unique</p>
                <p>
                  Catchy phrases, sayings, or expressions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase is-primary">Memorable</p>
                <p>
                  A marketable tag line, slogan, motto, or quote.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase is-primary">Searchable</p>
                <p>
                  Has common keywords or significant traffic.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase is-primary">Versatile</p>
                <p>
                  Multiple meanings and use cases.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="content margin-bottom-20">
              <h2>What are the benefits of renting?</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="flex-list">
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Earn money from unused domains.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Organically grow traffic from your renters.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Increase the likelihood of a sale.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-3">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">How it works.</h1>
            <%# <p>
              Our platform introduces your domain to potential renters. We create the listing page,
              set rental terms, manage payments and transactions, and handle the process of
              redirecting renter's content to the domain. This process is detailed below.
            </p>%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step One</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">You List Your Domain</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              Create custom listings using our upload tool and verify that you own them
              by pointing a DNS A Record to DomaHub.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Two</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">Someone Rents It</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              We pay you directly into a bank account you've linked
              with us. Rentals are not complete until we confirm payment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Three</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-share-square-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">We Redirect Web Content</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              The renter provides a link to some web content they wish to display and it is
              displayed on your domain for the duration of the rental.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
          <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Why list with DomaHub?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6">
